<div class="custom"  >
	<h1>How well do you understand your retailer’s technical needs?</h1>

<p>The current retail environment demands more of suppliers and growers meet exacting standards for quality, safety, sustainability and ethical issues. Matching manpower to these demands is always a challenge. PSI can provide the following services to assist:</p>

<ul class="article-list">
<li>Audit preparation and pre-inspections (BRC, Customer specific audits, Red Tractor Farm Assurance/Global GAP as well as Nurture, LEAF)</li>
<li>Provision of additional resource at times of peak demand eg NPD launches, completion of product safety packs for retailers</li>
<li>Expert problem solving to address non-conformances or corrective actions eg microbiological issues</li>
<li>Training and mentoring of existing less experienced team members</li>
<li>Auditing of suppliers for food safety (eg Pre-audits for BRC, IFS, TFMS)</li>
<li>Retailer specific auditing (eg M&S Field to Fork, Waitrose Farm Assessment)</li>
</ul>

<p>To find the right solution for you contact PSI on <strong>01189 888033</strong> or e-mail <a href="mailto:ian@psi-advantage.com" title="Mail PSI Advantage">ian@psi-advantage.com</a></p>
<br/>
